divs: sighting detailsi was driving down us hwy 377 2-3 miles north\northeast of dublin, texas looking to the south\southwest when i witnessed a long formation of blinking brights white lights which appeared to be directly over the top of us hwy 377. another area of the same pattern looked like it was directly over the city of dublin. these lights stretched over a mile to 2 miles radius in perfect formation. after about 10 minutes these lights ceased quickly. at the very end of this event i noticed 2 jets moving towards the areas where the lights had been. there has to be more witness'es to this event out there because the lights where over the city & over us hwy 377 'very populated areas of erath county.
